Usage
Run the agent:

bash
node agent.js
Example commands to try:

"Create a file hello.txt with 'Hello World'"

"List all files in this folder"

"Python script to calculate factorial of 5"

VS Code Extension (Bonus)
Open the vscode-extension folder in VS Code

Press F5 to launch extension development mode

Use the command palette (Ctrl+Shift+P) and run "Workik: Execute Task"

Technical Details
AI API: Groq (llama3-8b-8192 model)

Runtime: Node.js

Dependencies:

node-fetch for API calls

readline for user input

child_process for command execution

Future Improvements
Add local LLM fallback (Ollama)

Implement multi-step project generation

Add command history

Improve safety sandboxing
